<doc f='include/sys/wait.h' l='142'>/* Wait for a child to exit.  When one does, put its status in *STAT_LOC and
   return its process ID.  For errors return (pid_t) -1.  If USAGE is not
   nil, store information about the child&apos;s resource usage there.  If the
   WUNTRACED bit is set in OPTIONS, return status for stopped children;
   otherwise don&apos;t.  */</doc>
